      • convertACAQToImageJ

        Object convertACAQToImageJ(ACAQData acaqData,
                           boolean activate,
                           boolean noWindow,
                           String windowName)
        Converts an ACAQ5 data type to its corresponding ImageJ data type
        Parameters:
        acaqData - ACAQ data
        activate - If true, the data should be made visible in ImageJ
        noWindow - If true, the conversion should not create GUI windows
        windowName - Window name of the ImageJ data. Might be ignored or used otherwise to identify data.
        Returns:
        Converted object
